    <div class="col-sm-8" id="Student" style="display:block;">
        <h2 class="big-txt margin-top-l">How does Studypool work?</h2>
        <p>Studypool is an online marketplace that connects students with questions with tutors who can answer them.
           Using Studypool gives you access to thousands of verified tutors to help you with any question at any time.</p>
 
        <p>Stuck on a frustrating question? Our tutors got you covered!</p>
        <h4>Step 1</h4>
        <p>Sign up and post your academic question. Set a time limit and price range. Questions are free to post.</p>
        <h4>Step 2</h4>
        <p>Receive bids from verified tutors who wants to help you. Studypool will make a recommendation for which tutor we think is the best overall, but you are also free to make your own choice by comparing reviews, statistics, and profiles.</p>
        <h4>Step 3</h4>
        <p>Sit back and relax while your tutor works to explain and help you understand your question. You only pay if you are satisfied with their services.</p>
        <h3>Studypool features</h3>
        <h4>ENCRYPTED PRIVACY</h4>
        <p>Just like the privacy of working with tutors in real life, we give you the option to make your questions and answers 100% private.</p>
        <h4>CONTROL</h4>
        <p>Studypool gives you complete control over how you learn. Get help with any question you have. Our tutors are ready to help you on demand, 24/7.</p>
        <h4>QUALITY HELP</h4>
        <p>All tutors on our platform go through a strict background check to verify their education and authenticity. As we put a high emphasis on quality, tutors who does not perform well will be removed from the site.</p>
    </div>
