              <div>
                  <p>Earn money by tutoring students online. Simply provide explanations and help to their questions.</p>
                  <h4>How Does it Work?</h4>
                  <p>
                     Sign up and browse questions. Bid on questions you're interested in providing explanations and help for by suggesting a price and delivery time.
                     If the student would like to work with you, they will pay an advance payment of your requested price which will be held by Studypool while the question remains unsolved.
                   </p>
                   <p>Once the student has completed the payment you will be notified, and the tutoring session will begin.</p>
                   <p>During the session your job is to provide explanations and help the student solve their question within the time limit agreed upon.
                      Once the student is satisfied, your payment will be released to you.
